node.text: Took a little dip in the glacier water on todays adventure🤩⛰🦋💦🌊 a liiittle bit cold, but could definitely have been colder😅 swipe to see behind the scenes of how I took this photo! When I'm out on my own I just have to be creative. A tripod and timelapse/burst mode is perfect to capture shots on your own📸🤩 #Norway #Gopro #Glacier

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by KAROLINE FOSSE in Voss with @visitvoss, and @mittnorge. May be an image of 1 person, nature and grass.

node.text: A little piece of a Norwegian fairytale 🌿✨🌞⛰ this is one of the stops we had while paddleboarding at Lønavatnet! Lots of cows are running around here, but we didn't meet any hihi🐮 how pretty is this place?? #Norway #Gopro #Mittnorge

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by KAROLINE FOSSE in Voss with @visitvoss. May be an image of 1 person, lake, mountain and nature.

node.text: A little cooldown in a tiny river, overlooking Voss🤩✨⛰ I have yet to see a lot of this side of Voss - I live on the other side, which you can see behind me on the other side of the lake! This is in front of "Gråsido", the mountain I usually look at when I'm home😄⛰ how do you like the view?✨ #Norway #Sony #Mittnorge

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by KAROLINE FOSSE on August 01, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, nature and body of water.

node.text: What a loooovely paddle in the glossy and calm Lønavatnet😍 one of the local lakes nearby that I have yet to see more of! The mountain in the back is Lønahorgi🥰🌞⛰ who else would want to paddle here?🙌🏼 #Norway #Gopro #Mittnorge

node.text: Tired of the river content yet?😂💦💙🐟🐬 can't help it, but it's soooo pretty and I wanna share all the photos I have from these spots🙊 it looks like the sunny warm days are taking a break now though! soooo, I guess that means swimming in the rain instead haha💦 who else loves a rainy swim?🥰 #Norway #Gopro

node.text: Of all the places I've travelled and explored, I think this spot is the absolute coolest and prettiest place I know🤩🌞💙 me and @thereseleid randomly found it as we actually visited another spot, but decided to just check around the area! And it really paid off🤩 straight out of a fairytale✨ who else has found a hidden secret spot this summer?🥰 whenever you go someplace cool, ALWAYS check around if there's something unknown nearby😄  #Gopro #Norway #Summer
